  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">The new quad-core processor consists of two high-performance 1.5 GHz cores and two lower-power 1.2 GHz cores running simultaneously for optimal load balancing and power efficiency. With over 2x the speed and over 3x the graphics performance of the previous generation Fire HD, the new quad-core processor ensures faster app launch times, smooth games and videos, and better overall performance.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Designed for portability</h4>
