  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Front-facing camera</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Fire HD includes a front-facing camera that is perfect for Skype video calls and taking selfies to share via Facebook or email.</p>


			
