  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Enjoy and share</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">Relive your most memorable moments in HD. Our beautifully designed photo app makes it easy to view your albums or watch personal videos. Sharing your photos couldn't be easier—just tap on individual images to email or to post to Facebook or Twitter.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Free, unlimited cloud storage</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Photos taken with new Fire tablets are automatically backed-up wirelessly and available across Amazon devices and Cloud Drive apps so you have access anywhere. <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=201606470&amp;pop-up=1" target="_top">See details</a></p>


			
