  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">Rent or purchase the biggest new releases and the most popular titles from every major movie studio and TV network, including HBO, Warner, Fox, Sony, Disney, Lionsgate, MGM, Universal, Paramount, and more, plus Amazon Originals pilots and series. Stream instantly over Wi-Fi or download to enjoy later.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">X-Ray for movies and TV</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Fire tablets use the power of IMDb to bring Amazon's exclusive X-Ray service to movies and TV shows. Simply tap on any scene to instantly see which actors are currently on screen, jump to other movies in which they star, learn the names of songs as they play, see trivia questions and answers, and explore character backstories.</p>


			
