	<tbody><tr>
	<td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding ">

	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Huge music selection</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">With over 30 million songs from thousands of artists, the Amazon Digital Music Store brings all your favorite music to your fingertips. Music you buy on your Fire tablet is saved to Your Music Library for free, and you can play or download it anytime.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Prime Music</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Prime Music gives Prime members unlimited, ad-free access to over a million songs and hundreds of custom-built playlists. Load up your library with Prime Music. Find more music from your favorite artists or let Amazon's personalized recommendations introduce you to your next favorite band.</p>


			
	</td><td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding kmd-last-col">
	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">X-Ray for music</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">You can see lyrics that display line by line while you listen to many of your favorite songs. You can also explore a more immersive artist experience with more photos, videos, and fun facts than ever before. </p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Your music library</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Music you buy from Amazon is instantly available on all your devices—buy on your Fire tablet and listen right away with the Amazon Music app on your phone or your computer. Add your entire music collection to Amazon Music and start listening as soon as your Fire tablet arrives. Just tap Music on the home screen of your Fire tablet to manage your collection, play your music, or download it for offline playback.</p>




	</td>
	</tr>


