  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Our slim, form-fitting cases are designed to perfectly fit your Fire HD and provide full front and back protection. The cases are easy to attach and remove, and feature an integrated magnetic closure to ensure your case stays shut while on the go.
<br><br>
These innovative cases automatically put your Fire tablet to sleep when it is closed and wake it upon opening, saving battery life while making it easy to jump back into your apps, games, movies, and more. 
