  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Your work email and docs</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body "><b><i>New</i></b>—With WPS Office, create, edit, view, and print Word, Excel, and PowerPoint files on your Fire tablet. Check and reply to work email on-the-go with a robust Exchange email experience with ActiveSync.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Fire Keyboard</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last"><b><i>New</i></b>—Boost your productivity and get work done with Fire Keyboard, Amazon's own thin and light keyboard for a superior typing experience on Fire tablets. <a href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00KYFWDLU" target="_top">Learn more</a></p>


			
	</td><td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding kmd-last-col">
	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Fire tablets at the office</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">Bring your Fire HD or HDX to the office and get the most out of your tablet. You can connect to your corporate Wi-Fi network, get on your company's intranet, download files, submit expenses, and more. Take advantage of the Fire tablets rich selection of productivity and business apps.</p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Stay connected</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">With Fire tablets, you can stay connected whether you're at the office or away using remote VPN. Access your company's network on-the-go and keep your corporate data secure with encryption. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/feature.html?docId=1000658051" target="_top">Learn more</a></p>




