</p>


			
	</td><td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding kmd-last-col">
	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Save more, carry less</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Save up to 80% when you rent and up to 60% when you buy eTextbooks. Just because you carry a heavy college course load doesn't mean you need to carry a heavy textbook load too. You can also study smarter with features like X-Ray for Textbooks and Notebook. <a href="http://www.amazon.com/b?ie=UTF8&amp;node=2223210011" target="_top">Learn more</a></p>




