  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Content on hundreds of devices</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">At Amazon, we make it easy for you to access your content on other devices. The books, videos, apps, audiobooks, games, and music that you buy for your Fire tablet can also be enjoyed on Amazon apps for Windows, Mac, Android, iOS, game consoles, TVs, and more.</p>


			
	</td><td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding kmd-last-col">
	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Whispersync</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Start streaming a movie on your Fire tablet, pause, then resume watching the same scene on your TV. Whispersync remembers how much you've watched, read, listened, or played, so you can pick up right where you left off, no matter which device you are using.</p>




