	<td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding ">

	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Free cloud storage</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">With every Fire tablet, you get free, unlimited cloud storage for all your Amazon content including any photos you've taken with your Fire tablet, so you can rest easy knowing that you'll never accidently lose the content you love. </p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Store your music</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Import your entire music library to Amazon Music and play it on your Fire tablet—just tap "Music" on your homescreen to get started. Browse and search your library, create and manage playlists, play your music from the cloud, or download for offline playback. All your Amazon digital music purchases and your first 250 imported songs are stored free.</p>


			
	</td><td style="width: 50%;" class="kmd-standard-padding kmd-last-col">
	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Free unlimited cloud storage for photos</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body ">Your Fire tablet includes free unlimited storage in Amazon Cloud Drive for all photos taken with the device, 5 GB of storage for photos and files you upload from your phone and computer, and free storage for all Amazon content. Access all your Cloud Drive content on your Fire tablet by going to Photos and Docs. <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=201606470&amp;pop-up=1" target="_top">See details</a></p>


	

  <h4 class="kmd-paragraph-title">Cloud collections</h4>
  <p class="kmd-text-paragraph-body kmd-paragraph-last">Organize your content library into Collections like "Favorite Books" and "Sports Apps" that are synchronized with your other Kindle e-readers, Fire tablets, Fire Phone, and reading apps.</p>




